{"name": "flodger", "metadata": {"name": "flodger", "version": "1.0.3", "classifiers": ["License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Operating System :: OS Independent", "Programming Language :: Python :: 3"], "home_page": null, "license": null, "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["loguru", "pandas"], "summary": "A package for function-driven logging.", "upload_time": 1734357747}, "documentation": ["# flodger \nA package for function-driven logging.\n\nThe ethos of `flodger` is to have all logging within a project driven by\nfunction calls and function outputs.\n\nNo explicit log statements need inserting - just the addition of the `log_function_call`\ndecorator onto any and all functions that you want to log.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "flodger", "documentation": [], "functions": [], "variables": [], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "flodger.log_function_call", "xref": {"fqname": "flodger.flodger.log_function_call", "project": null}}, {"name": "flodger.setup", "xref": {"fqname": "flodger.flodger.setup", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "flodger.flodger", "documentation": [], "functions": [{"name": "flodger.flodger.setup", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "path", "type": {"name": "Path", "xref": {"fqname": "pathlib.Path", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "format", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Sets up the logger to log in the format we want.\n\nThis is done because technically every log entry is made from this file - and\nthe default format records only that.\n\nWe use our custom format here that removes that (and we add the actual \nfunction to the message itself)."]}, {"name": "flodger.flodger.log_function_call", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "level", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": "..."}, {"name": "**kwargs", "type": null, "default": null}], "returns": null, "documentation": ["Logs a function call.\n\nFor a decorated function, two log entries will be made:\n- When the function is initially called - including parameters\n- When the function returns - including parameters and the output\n\nAny parameter / return values that aren't appropriate to log are coerced to\na cleaner format.\n\nFor example, a DataFrame with 100 rows and 3 columns is represented by \"DataFrame<shape=(100, 3)>\".\n\nArgs:\n    level (str, default = 'DEBUG'):\n        The logging level to use. "]}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._get_function_call_str", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "function", "type": {"name": "callable", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "args", "type": {"name": "tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "kwargs", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._get_function_call_params_str", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "args", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "kwargs", "type": {"name": "dict", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.dict", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._get_output_str", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "output", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "function_call_str", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._get_error_str", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "error", "type": {"name": "Exception", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.Exception", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "function_call_str", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._coerce_value", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "value", "type": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._coerce_str", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "value", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._coerce_basic_iterable", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "value", "type": {"name": "list | set | tuple | dict", "xref": null, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": []}, {"name": "flodger.flodger._coerce_dataframe", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "value", "type": {"name": "pd.DataFrame", "xref": {"fqname": "pandas.DataFrame", "project": "pandas"}, "params": null}, "default": null}, {"name": "package", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "proj